name: Bmegrad
tagline: Website for the Biomedical Engineering Graduate Students' Club at the National University of Singapore
body:
### Hello

Welcome to the development page for the website of the Biomedical Engineering Graduate Students' Club at the National University of Singapore

You can make a local copy of the website for evaluation purposes. Please note that the artwork, photos, and other content still belong to their respective owners, and unauthorised distribution of such files may amount to copyright infringement.

### Clone URL
```
$ https://github.com/kknundy/bmegrad.git
```

### Authors and Contributors
Currently maintained by @kknundy ([site](http://kknundy.net)). 
Inputs from Aishwarya Bandla and [Rizwan](http://www.researchism.com/).

### Support or Contact
If you encounter any issues with the site, please contact us through the [issues page](https://github.com/kknundy/bmegrad/issues) of this Github repo.
